From a4f6a846ffce0233f16b3498bd51734827d7ed63 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sun, 1 Mar 2026 19:08:52 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 51/51] Issue 694: Replace pane_id with tab_id
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The pane_id wandered far from home,
Through strings and buffers forced to roam.
Now tab_id reigns with integer grace—
An int64 in pane_id's place.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
